sentences: Baek Ye-rin (Korean:백예린; born June 26, 1997), also credited as Yerin Baek, is a South Korean singer-songwriter.
A former member of duo 15&, she debuted as a solo artist with the mini album Frank, in 2015.
Known for her delicate and sweet vocals, since 2015, she has had eight singles peak in the top ten on Gaon Digital Chart.
In addition to her solo career, she is also the front person for Korean rock band The Volunteers and has been performing with them from 2018 onwards.
Baek was born on June 26, 1997, in Jung District, Daejeon.
